  "texts": [
    "3 Classification of DL-based algorithms for TSP.",
    "4.3 DL-based end-to-end construction algorithms DL-based end-to-end construction algorithms typically utilize neural networks to learn constructive policies and autonomously generate a complete solution step-by-step from scratch. 4.",
    "232Transformer-based algorithms Due to Transformer's high quality, parallelization capabilities, and strong generalization performance, It was applied to solving TSP.",
    "• Multi-head Attention + RL algorithm In 2018, Deudon et al. [49] utilized Transformer to propose their algorithm.",
    "Their model adopts an encoder-decoder architecture."
  ]
}